<step><![CDATA[fry yardlong beans, for 4m, until tender, then set aside]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[sitr fry chilies with the pork high heat]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add pickled cabbage, spring onions for 20s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add light soy sauce, sugar, rice wine, water and stir in briefly before serving]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
